          "title": "Cookies and similar technologies",
          "content": {
            "type": "root",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "p",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "We use cookies and similar technologies on webblyhosting.com and in our control panel/client area to:"
                  }
